<problem id="fs-idm217527344">
<para id="fs-idm479213584"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68115"/>A company sells small motors as a component part to automobiles. The Model 101 motor sells for $850 and has per-unit variable costs of $400 associated with its production. The company has fixed expenses of $90,000 per month. In August, the company sold 425 of the Model 101 motors.</para>
